1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 23]

2
00:00:16,046 --> 00:00:19,525
[Zhou's residence]

3
00:00:20,126 --> 00:00:20,925
This month,

4
00:00:21,846 --> 00:00:23,325
all Zhou family affairs you managed

5
00:00:23,326 --> 00:00:24,845
have been transferred to a designated person.

6
00:00:27,606 --> 00:00:28,725
Take this money.

7
00:00:29,126 --> 00:00:29,965
I don't want money,

8
00:00:30,846 --> 00:00:31,485
Master.

9
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:33,605
I was planning to leave,

10
00:00:34,646 --> 00:00:35,285
but...

11
00:00:36,686 --> 00:00:38,565
I was sold by my brother.

12
00:00:38,806 --> 00:00:40,165
If I go back now,

13
00:00:40,446 --> 00:00:42,285
he'll just sell me again.

14
00:00:44,126 --> 00:00:44,885
Before

15
00:00:45,446 --> 00:00:47,445
he almost sold me to a brothel.

16
00:00:48,446 --> 00:00:49,325
This time...

17
00:00:55,286 --> 00:00:56,085
Master,

18
00:00:56,646 --> 00:00:58,325
I truly have nowhere to go.

19
00:00:58,966 --> 00:01:00,405
I can work in the kitchen.

20
00:01:00,726 --> 00:01:02,965
I won't get in your or Ms. Ye's way.

21
00:01:03,406 --> 00:01:04,205
Master,

22
00:01:05,086 --> 00:01:06,045
I beg you,

23
00:01:06,446 --> 00:01:07,405
I beg you!

24
00:01:07,646 --> 00:01:08,405
Master!

25
00:01:08,966 --> 00:01:10,405
She has been here for so many years,

26
00:01:10,726 --> 00:01:12,165
if not merit, there's hard work.

27
00:01:12,846 --> 00:01:14,325
A woman wandering the streets,

28
00:01:14,966 --> 00:01:16,485
even with the money you gave,

29
00:01:16,686 --> 00:01:17,765
it may not last.

30
00:01:18,046 --> 00:01:19,285
You must leave.

31
00:01:27,606 --> 00:01:28,325
Nanxi.

32
00:01:28,606 --> 00:01:29,325
Nanxi!

33
00:01:39,326 --> 00:01:40,205
Nothing serious.

34
00:01:41,646 --> 00:01:42,765
The pregnant woman was just

35
00:01:43,326 --> 00:01:44,445
overwhelmed emotionally,

36
00:01:44,566 --> 00:01:45,485
got too worked up,

37
00:01:45,726 --> 00:01:46,405
and passed out.

38
00:01:46,686 --> 00:01:47,725
What did you say?

39
00:01:48,966 --> 00:01:49,765
Pregnant?

40
00:01:50,366 --> 00:01:51,045
From now on,

41
00:01:51,046 --> 00:01:52,805
ensure she gets peaceful rest.

42
00:01:53,566 --> 00:01:54,405
Absolutely avoid

43
00:01:54,526 --> 00:01:56,285
extreme emotional highs and lows.

44
00:01:56,766 --> 00:01:58,045
She's with child?

45
00:01:58,686 --> 00:01:59,885
I'm certain of it.

46
00:02:00,326 --> 00:02:01,245
The pregnant woman herself

47
00:02:01,246 --> 00:02:02,525
is physically weak and cold.

48
00:02:02,526 --> 00:02:03,485
Pregnant...

49
00:02:03,526 --> 00:02:04,765
This pregnancy

50
00:02:04,846 --> 00:02:06,405
is a heaven-sent opportunity.

51
00:02:06,686 --> 00:02:07,885
Since she's conceived,

52
00:02:08,046 --> 00:02:09,205
care for the fetus diligently.

53
00:02:21,086 --> 00:02:21,845
Master,

54
00:02:22,686 --> 00:02:23,685
I'm pregnant.

55
00:02:29,606 --> 00:02:30,805
The doctor just said

56
00:02:31,766 --> 00:02:33,245
conception was extremely difficult for me.

57
00:02:35,486 --> 00:02:36,365
I must keep

58
00:02:38,046 --> 00:02:39,165
this child.

59
00:02:42,886 --> 00:02:43,525
Keep it?

60
00:02:45,246 --> 00:02:46,365
In what capacity?

61
00:02:48,246 --> 00:02:48,925
Master,

62
00:02:50,366 --> 00:02:51,885
I'm just a woman.

63
00:02:53,366 --> 00:02:54,605
Women have no way to rise above

64
00:02:54,926 --> 00:02:56,565
in this chaotic world.

65
00:02:59,646 --> 00:03:01,605
What's the point of so much education?

66
00:03:02,486 --> 00:03:04,245
In the end, we still become wives

67
00:03:04,246 --> 00:03:04,765
and mothers.

68
00:03:04,766 --> 00:03:05,525
Isn't that so?

69
00:03:06,886 --> 00:03:07,645
Master.

70
00:03:08,526 --> 00:03:11,765
You're the only person we can

71
00:03:12,526 --> 00:03:13,725
rely on.

72
00:03:16,246 --> 00:03:17,885
Even if Ye Zhiqiu doesn't marry me,

73
00:03:19,686 --> 00:03:20,925
I won't marry you either.

74
00:03:35,046 --> 00:03:36,045
Child,

75
00:03:37,166 --> 00:03:39,365
I will make your father

76
00:03:40,086 --> 00:03:42,525
marry me willingly.

77
00:03:45,326 --> 00:03:46,925
This is the He family bloodline.

78
00:03:47,206 --> 00:03:48,725
You say you'll abandon it just like that?

79
00:03:48,966 --> 00:03:50,485
I cannot keep this child.

80
00:03:51,446 --> 00:03:52,485
Yimo,

81
00:03:53,046 --> 00:03:55,845
our He-family line is dwindling now.

82
00:03:56,566 --> 00:03:57,965
Now that you have offspring,

83
00:03:58,246 --> 00:04:00,325
it's a great blessing.

84
00:04:00,446 --> 00:04:01,965
Even though the child's mother

85
00:04:02,086 --> 00:04:03,445
was a maidservant,

86
00:04:03,446 --> 00:04:04,525
that doesn't matter.

87
00:04:05,726 --> 00:04:08,125
As long as she bears a boy this time,

88
00:04:08,526 --> 00:04:10,045
I'll make her your concubine.

89
00:04:10,566 --> 00:04:11,845
Then find the child

90
00:04:11,846 --> 00:04:14,125
a proper mother of noble status

91
00:04:14,126 --> 00:04:15,245
to raise him.

92
00:04:16,126 --> 00:04:17,885
There won't be any problems.

93
00:04:18,526 --> 00:04:19,685
In this life,

94
00:04:20,046 --> 00:04:21,445
I'll only marry Ye Zhiqiu.

95
00:04:22,246 --> 00:04:23,565
Look at you.

96
00:04:23,886 --> 00:04:26,565
Look at yourself!

97
00:04:26,646 --> 00:04:28,925
You're completely out of control.

98
00:04:30,846 --> 00:04:31,565
Matriarch He,

99
00:04:31,846 --> 00:04:32,605
don't be angry.

100
00:04:32,646 --> 00:04:33,205
Sit down.

101
00:04:35,246 --> 00:04:37,485
Master is young at heart,

102
00:04:37,686 --> 00:04:39,405
just dreaming of romance now.

103
00:04:39,526 --> 00:04:40,765
Reasoning won't work with him.

104
00:04:41,326 --> 00:04:43,005
You're quite open-minded.

105
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:46,845
Having served Master for years,

106
00:04:47,366 --> 00:04:48,125
I know

107
00:04:48,326 --> 00:04:48,885
he's not truly

108
00:04:48,886 --> 00:04:50,485
unwilling to keep this child,

109
00:04:51,046 --> 00:04:52,045
but rather

110
00:04:52,766 --> 00:04:53,725
because of that

111
00:04:53,766 --> 00:04:55,765
Fifth Concubine who married his father.

112
00:04:57,046 --> 00:04:58,125
What do you mean?

113
00:04:59,646 --> 00:05:01,045
First, make the Fifth Concubine

114
00:05:01,366 --> 00:05:02,565
back down.

115
00:05:09,446 --> 00:05:10,885
[Zhongshan Hospital]

116
00:05:11,446 --> 00:05:12,365
Next patient.

117
00:05:19,126 --> 00:05:19,885
Slowly.

118
00:05:20,966 --> 00:05:21,885
Ms. Ye,

119
00:05:22,366 --> 00:05:24,125
I know you're hiding in the hospital

120
00:05:24,286 --> 00:05:25,645
to avoid seeing Yimo.

121
00:05:26,526 --> 00:05:27,605
Rest assured,

122
00:05:27,846 --> 00:05:29,245
I won't tell him.

123
00:05:34,166 --> 00:05:35,205
Matriarch He, it must have taken

124
00:05:36,766 --> 00:05:37,885
some effort for you to come see me, right?

125
00:05:38,846 --> 00:05:39,845
Not too difficult.

126
00:05:40,886 --> 00:05:42,925
This hospital belongs to the He family.

127
00:05:43,646 --> 00:05:45,765
Getting the director to tell the truth

128
00:05:45,846 --> 00:05:46,605
isn't hard.

129
00:05:50,926 --> 00:05:52,565
What illness are you dealing with?

130
00:05:52,806 --> 00:05:53,845
No illness.

131
00:05:54,566 --> 00:05:55,525
I came specially

132
00:05:55,646 --> 00:05:56,805
to find you.

133
00:05:57,886 --> 00:05:58,885
Since you're not ill,

134
00:05:58,886 --> 00:05:59,965
please leave first.

135
00:06:00,046 --> 00:06:01,165
Many patients are waiting.

136
00:06:01,606 --> 00:06:02,525
Ms. Ye,

137
00:06:03,046 --> 00:06:04,445
I know you used to be

138
00:06:04,566 --> 00:06:07,285
Fifth Concubine to Yimo's father.

139
00:06:08,326 --> 00:06:09,285
By rights,

140
00:06:10,126 --> 00:06:12,485
I wouldn't approve of you and Yimo.

141
00:06:13,286 --> 00:06:14,805
But Yimo

142
00:06:15,246 --> 00:06:16,765
is pure-hearted.

143
00:06:17,166 --> 00:06:19,645
I don't want a woman

144
00:06:19,886 --> 00:06:21,285
to cause discord

145
00:06:21,966 --> 00:06:23,565
between us.

146
00:06:24,486 --> 00:06:26,845
Though I won't oppose your relationship,

147
00:06:27,646 --> 00:06:30,525
it doesn't mean I've accepted you.

148
00:06:31,766 --> 00:06:33,805
When you're with Yimo later,

149
00:06:33,806 --> 00:06:35,805
you must counsel him well

150
00:06:35,966 --> 00:06:38,685
to expand our He family lineage.

151
00:06:39,806 --> 00:06:41,805
That maid named Nanxi,

152
00:06:42,686 --> 00:06:44,685
since she's carrying Yimo's child,

153
00:06:44,886 --> 00:06:46,525
you should help Yimo

154
00:06:46,526 --> 00:06:48,165
handle this matter.

155
00:06:48,726 --> 00:06:50,325
Coming from a maid background,

156
00:06:50,846 --> 00:06:53,405
she could never affect your status.

157
00:06:53,846 --> 00:06:55,765
You should show some tolerance.

158
00:06:56,206 --> 00:06:57,445
Don't take advantage of

159
00:06:58,246 --> 00:06:59,605
Yimo's affection for you

160
00:06:59,726 --> 00:07:01,525
to become arrogant and jealous.

161
00:07:02,406 --> 00:07:03,485
Do you understand?

162
00:07:06,526 --> 00:07:07,365
I understand.

163
00:07:08,766 --> 00:07:10,525
Matriarch He, you're getting senile

164
00:07:11,286 --> 00:07:12,245
and having delusions.

165
00:07:13,606 --> 00:07:14,605
But this condition

166
00:07:14,966 --> 00:07:15,765
is beyond my expertise.

167
00:07:16,246 --> 00:07:16,925
Exit and turn left

168
00:07:17,126 --> 00:07:17,965
to the psychiatry department.

169
00:07:18,286 --> 00:07:19,365
What do you mean by this?

170
00:07:21,806 --> 00:07:23,005
Your family affairs

171
00:07:23,206 --> 00:07:24,245
have nothing to do with me,

172
00:07:24,246 --> 00:07:25,205
a poor working girl.

173
00:07:25,926 --> 00:07:27,805
Nanxi is pregnant with the Zhou family heir.

174
00:07:28,526 --> 00:07:30,365
How can an outsider like me help?

175
00:07:31,206 --> 00:07:32,045
Matriarch He,

176
00:07:32,806 --> 00:07:33,805
I need to continue working.

177
00:07:34,046 --> 00:07:34,765
Goodbye.

178
00:07:36,526 --> 00:07:40,525
So you're refusing the easy way.

179
00:07:41,246 --> 00:07:42,365
Are you going to attack me,

180
00:07:42,366 --> 00:07:44,165
a doctor, inside the hospital?

181
00:07:44,166 --> 00:07:44,885
NO,

182
00:07:45,206 --> 00:07:46,405
I won't lay hands on you.

183
00:07:47,806 --> 00:07:48,685
Ms. Ye,

184
00:07:48,966 --> 00:07:51,365
you'll have to leave this hospital eventually.

185
00:07:51,806 --> 00:07:52,605
For instance,

186
00:07:52,766 --> 00:07:54,525
on your way home from work,

187
00:07:54,926 --> 00:07:56,685
while grocery shopping...

188
00:07:57,446 --> 00:07:59,525
accidents can happen.

189
00:08:01,686 --> 00:08:02,965
Are you threatening me?

190
00:08:03,326 --> 00:08:05,685
Just giving you a friendly reminder.

191
00:08:14,806 --> 00:08:15,805
I heard

192
00:08:16,326 --> 00:08:17,965
someone's causing trouble at the hospital.

193
00:08:19,326 --> 00:08:20,085
Our guns

194
00:08:20,406 --> 00:08:21,605
don't discriminate.

195
00:08:23,566 --> 00:08:25,085
Everyone's here for consultations.

196
00:08:26,526 --> 00:08:27,165
Dr. Ye,

197
00:08:27,286 --> 00:08:28,485
is this old lady finished?

198
00:08:29,166 --> 00:08:30,485
We're still waiting our turn.

199
00:08:31,686 --> 00:08:32,405
Finished.

200
00:08:34,806 --> 00:08:36,205
Keep the Zhou family's dirty laundry

201
00:08:36,526 --> 00:08:38,325
away from innocent people.

202
00:08:39,046 --> 00:08:39,965
Dr. Ye

203
00:08:40,406 --> 00:08:41,565
is under my protection.

204
00:08:42,406 --> 00:08:43,325
If your He family

205
00:08:43,526 --> 00:08:45,205
dares oppose me...

206
00:08:48,286 --> 00:08:50,245
consider your strength carefully.

207
00:08:51,086 --> 00:08:52,365
As you said,

208
00:08:53,526 --> 00:08:54,525
accidents

209
00:08:55,366 --> 00:08:56,885
can happen unexpectedly.

210
00:09:19,326 --> 00:09:20,405
Thanks for earlier.

211
00:09:24,886 --> 00:09:25,885
I've heard everything

212
00:09:26,406 --> 00:09:27,325
about the Zhou family.

213
00:09:28,486 --> 00:09:29,725
I'll increase security

214
00:09:30,126 --> 00:09:31,125
to protect you.

215
00:09:33,486 --> 00:09:34,965
Why such a big production?

216
00:09:35,646 --> 00:09:37,685
Matriarch He's just talking tough.

217
00:09:38,166 --> 00:09:39,885
She won't actually do anything.

218
00:09:40,086 --> 00:09:40,805
Your actions

219
00:09:40,966 --> 00:09:42,605
will scare away patients.

220
00:09:42,766 --> 00:09:43,725
I don't care.

221
00:09:44,926 --> 00:09:46,285
I only care about your safety.

222
00:10:02,486 --> 00:10:03,405
Smash it all!

223
00:10:11,326 --> 00:10:12,205
Yu Shi'an,

224
00:10:12,206 --> 00:10:13,485
have you gone mad?

225
00:10:14,246 --> 00:10:15,205
Is your family insane?

226
00:10:15,206 --> 00:10:16,965
Like a rabid dog biting everyone?

227
00:10:17,526 --> 00:10:18,405
What do you mean?

228
00:10:18,406 --> 00:10:19,485
Smashing your dock this time

229
00:10:19,486 --> 00:10:20,605
is just a lesson for you.

230
00:10:21,246 --> 00:10:22,165
Next time,

231
00:10:22,446 --> 00:10:24,005
if that old hag Matriarch He

232
00:10:24,126 --> 00:10:25,765
dares to trouble Ye Xiaoman again,

233
00:10:25,966 --> 00:10:27,365
I'll burn down all the businesses

234
00:10:27,366 --> 00:10:28,365
of Zhou and He families.

235
00:10:31,286 --> 00:10:32,285
What happened to my grandma?

236
00:10:32,806 --> 00:10:34,645
I'll protect Ye Xiaoman from now on.

237
00:10:36,566 --> 00:10:37,685
Understood?

238
00:10:39,366 --> 00:10:40,085
Let's go.

239
00:10:51,726 --> 00:10:52,525
Nanxi.

240
00:10:53,446 --> 00:10:55,245
You really enjoy sour foods.

241
00:10:56,126 --> 00:10:57,325
Yes, Matriarch.

242
00:10:57,686 --> 00:10:58,685
I don't know why,

243
00:10:58,806 --> 00:10:59,525
lately,

244
00:10:59,966 --> 00:11:01,365
I suddenly crave sour things.

245
00:11:09,166 --> 00:11:09,965
Grandma.

246
00:11:11,166 --> 00:11:12,445
Why didn't you tell me

247
00:11:12,446 --> 00:11:13,205
before going to her?

248
00:11:13,846 --> 00:11:14,845
Because of Nanxi,

249
00:11:14,846 --> 00:11:16,405
she's been cold to me lately.

250
00:11:18,526 --> 00:11:19,485
Your interference

251
00:11:20,326 --> 00:11:22,365
will only make things worse.

252
00:11:22,366 --> 00:11:23,525
You call this interference?

253
00:11:23,966 --> 00:11:26,485
I'm the matriarch of the He family.

254
00:11:26,686 --> 00:11:28,525
For me to visit

255
00:11:28,606 --> 00:11:30,525
a concubine serving as a maid to negotiate

256
00:11:30,846 --> 00:11:32,085
is already giving her

257
00:11:32,086 --> 00:11:33,485
the greatest honor.

258
00:11:33,726 --> 00:11:34,885
What more could she want?

259
00:11:36,246 --> 00:11:37,605
I've seen plenty of women

260
00:11:37,606 --> 00:11:39,205
like her before.

261
00:11:39,566 --> 00:11:41,085
She's just taking advantage

262
00:11:41,286 --> 00:11:42,725
of your minor mistake,

263
00:11:43,486 --> 00:11:44,645
putting on airs

264
00:11:44,806 --> 00:11:47,085
to gain more benefits for herself.

265
00:11:51,126 --> 00:11:52,685
Please stop interfering in my affairs.

266
00:11:52,686 --> 00:11:53,445
Okay?

267
00:12:01,366 --> 00:12:02,285
Matriarch, please calm down.

268
00:12:02,686 --> 00:12:03,605
Master, please calm down.

269
00:12:04,406 --> 00:12:05,365
All the fault

270
00:12:06,166 --> 00:12:07,565
is mine.

271
00:12:09,526 --> 00:12:10,845
I don't want any status.

272
00:12:11,806 --> 00:12:13,845
I only ask to safely deliver this child.

273
00:12:15,206 --> 00:12:16,485
I can continue serving as a maid

274
00:12:16,486 --> 00:12:17,365
in this household.

275
00:12:18,286 --> 00:12:19,005
Even if...

276
00:12:19,686 --> 00:12:21,005
even if we don't tell the child

277
00:12:21,686 --> 00:12:23,085
who his mother is.

278
00:12:26,686 --> 00:12:27,445
Master...

279
00:12:27,486 --> 00:12:29,565
Master, I beg you!

280
00:12:30,246 --> 00:12:31,965
You're quite obedient.

281
00:12:32,246 --> 00:12:33,205
Rest assured,

282
00:12:33,766 --> 00:12:36,085
if you bear me a boy,

283
00:12:36,326 --> 00:12:37,805
I'll see to it

284
00:12:38,046 --> 00:12:39,525
that you're elevated to concubine.

285
00:12:39,886 --> 00:12:41,645
Stop interfering in my affairs!

286
00:12:41,766 --> 00:12:42,605
You're being absurd!

287
00:12:43,166 --> 00:12:43,925
Grandma!

288
00:12:45,526 --> 00:12:46,685
I beg you.

289
00:12:47,446 --> 00:12:48,965
Stop going to find Ye Zhiqiu.

290
00:12:49,366 --> 00:12:50,165
Okay?

291
00:12:50,646 --> 00:12:51,925
Seems I have no authority

292
00:12:51,926 --> 00:12:54,365
in this household anymore.

293
00:12:55,566 --> 00:12:56,365
Zhou Yimo,

294
00:12:56,886 --> 00:12:58,045
you've grown up.

295
00:12:58,646 --> 00:12:59,965
You've grown quite the nerve, haven't you?

296
00:13:00,526 --> 00:13:02,045
You don't need me anymore?

297
00:13:03,206 --> 00:13:04,205
Let me tell you,

298
00:13:04,646 --> 00:13:05,685
this matter

299
00:13:05,766 --> 00:13:07,205
is settled!

300
00:13:18,326 --> 00:13:18,805
Hurry!

301
00:13:19,046 --> 00:13:19,685
Help her up.

302
00:13:19,806 --> 00:13:20,405
Yes.

303
00:13:25,526 --> 00:13:27,525
Don't tire out my precious grandson.

304
00:13:28,286 --> 00:13:29,165
Don't worry.

305
00:13:29,686 --> 00:13:31,565
As long as you give me a grandson,

306
00:13:32,446 --> 00:13:34,085
I'll stand up for you.

307
00:13:36,766 --> 00:13:37,965
Yes, Matriarch.

308
00:13:39,806 --> 00:13:40,365
Go ahead.

309
00:13:40,366 --> 00:13:41,165
Eat.
